  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "JuAC4s82hMbNkRqX17s0ltqjVmeI/HhsmWljgf+i7Kg=",
    "originContent": "### Installation",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "npm을 사용하는 경우, `npm install @saehrimnir/druidjs`로 설치하고 다음과 같이 사용하십시오."
  },
  {
    "row": 35,
    "rowsha": "wZnLptIfIuS2vJQFGG39nbQB5TGcmXOHYNKhlDNkSdo=",
    "originContent": "If you use npm, install with `npm install @saehrimnir/druidjs`, and use it with",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 36,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 37,
    "rowsha": "6IXHjyAaUImYsJ5BaklYyXzUO0AADdWSuW9x1J7wxDQ=",
    "originContent": "```js",
    "translatedContent": "```js"
  },
  {
    "row": 38,
    "rowsha": "pY1xPKCrk+75KIQDMEHs2Gp/kXAf/WeE2JYXQ3r5sjE=",
    "originContent": "import * as druid from \"@saehrimnir/druidjs\";",
    "translatedContent": "import * as druid from \"@saehrimnir/druidjs\";"
  },
  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "zHRwffGnpBY76tmPUwUd42glVE8MmtviO/CIYS6ZsPk=",
    "originContent": "Otherwise download the files [here](https://github.com/saehm/DruidJS/releases/latest), or use for instance [unpkg](https://unpkg.com/@saehrimnir/druidjs) this way:",
    "translatedContent": "그렇지 않으면 [여기](https://github.com/saehm/DruidJS/releases/latest)에서 파일을 다운로드하거나, 예를 들어 [unpkg](https://unpkg.com/@saehrimnir/druidjs)를 다음과 같이 사용하세요:"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "Uc5+AjuMoqnnDSvMf+9u+CTVledsHCbqDg0MxKvxsYw=",
    "originContent": "```html",
    "translatedContent": "```html"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "v+z16d6rDAjSOuznhevgx7O4bhiotEHaYePer8ZVxD0=",
    "originContent": "<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@saehrimnir/druidjs\"></script>",
    "translatedContent": "<script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@saehrimnir/druidjs\"></script>"
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "### 행렬"
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "k0mA1vwI0wpnahSfjJ5J+cVNstxtnneSFYy0918aCuI=",
    "originContent": "### Matrix",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "DruidJS는 내부적으로 데이터를 저장하기 위해 Matrix 클래스를 사용합니다. 예를 들어 `from` 함수를 사용하여 `druid.Matrix` 객체를 생성하여 사용할 수 있습니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "RLmL2J04KBAQ2CgQYTILCpLa3awuKJMxi4CM94st5xw=",
    "originContent": "DruidJS uses internally the Matrix class for storing data. You can use it by creating a `druid.Matrix` object for instance with the function `from`, in example:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "6IXHjyAaUImYsJ5BaklYyXzUO0AADdWSuW9x1J7wxDQ=",
    "originContent": "```js",
    "translatedContent": "```js"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "c7BQWFMhBwfYG5WuQgc0mCxllGAFYDTZsAW72IF/ABU=",
    "originContent": "import * as druid from '@saehrimnir/druidjs';",
    "translatedContent": "import * as druid from '@saehrimnir/druidjs';"
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "F3qR8K2yF7zqFtEU7V6uEXwI0G7NA04UgZwEMNbgpvY=",
    "originContent": "let data = [[...], [...], ...];",
    "translatedContent": "let data = [[...], [...], ...];"
  },
  {
    "row": 55,
    "rowsha": "llFfYqgb45LBI97KihRjRM52gZ2VRHWqlKMh8Ayd+IA=",
    "originContent": "let matrix = druid.Matrix.from(data);",
    "translatedContent": "let matrix = druid.Matrix.from(data);"
  },
  {
    "row": 56,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "zImQgp+W46tZN/yGC19JJsSlVETwwe2pmwgsYQTNBxw=",
    "originContent": "You can create a `druid.Matrix` object programmatically by:",
    "translatedContent": "다음과 같이 프로그래밍 방식으로 `druid.Matrix` 객체를 생성할 수 있습니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "6IXHjyAaUImYsJ5BaklYyXzUO0AADdWSuW9x1J7wxDQ=",
    "originContent": "```js",
    "translatedContent": "```js"
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "YD763iqshFLdhQvidq/kExpp0965QoK/veRQkLELQ6U=",
    "originContent": "let fn = (row, col) => (row == col ? 1 : 0);",
    "translatedContent": "let fn = (row, col) => (row == col ? 1 : 0);"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "RcTtJeB4Y7/B3h9km1VJmwL5tIKM0/YsUQsSoqwrYbQ=",
    "originContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(rows, columns, fn);",
    "translatedContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(rows, columns, fn);"
  },
  {
    "row": 63,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 64,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 65,
    "rowsha": "w1hbak6cxej/V/i/jTLTY1paLPFokYJjkyShHKF9gYQ=",
    "originContent": "If `rows == columns`, then `matrix` would be a identity matrix.",
    "translatedContent": "만약 `rows == columns` 이면, `matrix` 는 항등 행렬이 됩니다."
  },
  {
    "row": 66,
    "rowsha": "O6MhiZM2PL1tYlHUeHOg1u2hU18kB7kieJp8MWymOj8=",
    "originContent": "A shortcut for a identity matrix is:",
    "translatedContent": "항등 행렬의 단축 표기법은 다음과 같습니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 67,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 68,
    "rowsha": "6IXHjyAaUImYsJ5BaklYyXzUO0AADdWSuW9x1J7wxDQ=",
    "originContent": "```js",
    "translatedContent": "```js"
  },
  {
    "row": 69,
    "rowsha": "lC1RO4tlM8ch1+UQAkT+gGjaKtqtEIUkBmvJIrKgChs=",
    "originContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(rows, columns, \"I\");",
    "translatedContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(rows, columns, \"I\");"
  },
  {
    "row": 70,
    "rowsha": "U8nX4/7qeeOEVKc5G5zp7nhH9hdP7onP55ivPRofMTg=",
    "originContent": "// or",
    "translatedContent": "// or"
  },
  {
    "row": 71,
    "rowsha": "Q+2KcV7+DM0eYW108p+iV/99gYnbKhxIrrgvFj1hupo=",
    "originContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(rows, columnbs, \"identity\");",
    "translatedContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(rows, columnbs, \"identity\");"
  },
  {
    "row": 72,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
    "originContent": "```",
    "translatedContent": "```"
  },
  {
    "row": 73,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "행렬을 생성하는 더 많은 단축키가 있습니다:"
  },
  {
    "row": 74,
    "rowsha": "A/QucXmffOMmA4u1Vn0HGuxhvCTvu52mWQ2CahH0aV4=",
    "originContent": "There are more shortcuts for creating matrices:",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 75,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 76,
    "rowsha": "6IXHjyAaUImYsJ5BaklYyXzUO0AADdWSuW9x1J7wxDQ=",
    "originContent": "```js",
    "translatedContent": "```js"
  },
  {
    "row": 77,
    "rowsha": "DFv20ZZQq8FsPjCxCULdzJrZHrWL3aSSfL6/dnOpJXQ=",
    "originContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(3, 3, \"zeros\"); // matrix would be a 3x3 matrix with zeroes",
    "translatedContent": "let matrix = new druid.Matrix(3, 3, \"zeros\"); // matrix would be a 3x3 matrix with zeroes"
  },
